&lt;h4 id="pricing-framework"&gt;Pricing Framework&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;price floor(0 profit for producer): variable cost + allocated fixed cost&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;price celling (0 profit for customer): most value someone can obtain (what I can provide to customer)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;between floor &amp;amp; celling: determine price range -&amp;gt; compare w/ competitors. Might not use substitutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
